OL,6,FChristin Richards from Magellan said:
OL,7,F"We have reprocessed these images and
OL,8,Fwe have tried to share them inside
OL,9,Fthis game in the same way that we see
OL,10,Fthem every day through the lens of an
OL,11,FROV pilot."
OL,13,FMagellan's Thomas Holt said: "It's
OL,14,Ffaithful to the Titanic as it was in
OL,15,F2022 but obviously time hasn't been
OL,16,Fkind to it but you can still see it as
OL,17,Fit is, and there are still tonnes of
OL,18,Frecognisable features of it and then
OL,19,Fcombine that with the library and the
OL,20,Finformation about the various parts
OL,21,Fyou're scanning as you through it.
