OL,6,F"I think it's a pretty all-round
OL,7,Feducational and entertaining
OL,8,Fexperience because you can still go
OL,9,Fand discover as if you're really
OL,10,Fthere."
OL,12,FThe game is downloadable and allows
OL,13,Fusers to explore the ship's bow.
OL,15,FSenior Remote Operated Vehicle Pilot
OL,16,FGregor Young said: "Very few people
OL,17,Fget the opportunity to visit the wreck
OL,18,Fsite itself, so actually giving people
OL,19,Fthe opportunity to experience it, that
OL,20,Fis a big thing.
