OL,6,F"There is the human tragedy as well,
OL,7,Fyou'll see people's belongings and
OL,8,Fthat's the thing that touches you the
OL,9,Fmost when you're scouring the sea bed
OL,10,Fand having a look through the cameras."
OL,12,FIt's believed that around 1,500 people
OL,13,Fdied when the Titanic sank on 15 April
OL,14,F1912.
