OL,4,Ccreates interactive Titanic experience
OL,6,FDescendants of people who were on
OL,7,Fboard the Titanic have had the chance
OL,8,Fto see the game, Rosie Boleat said:
OL,9,F"It is incredible really to think that
OL,10,Fmy descendant was in there right at
OL,11,Fthe bottom really because he was a
OL,12,Fstoker, he got out and he saved a lot
OL,13,Fof people.
OL,15,FMagellan says there is more to come
OL,16,Fbut for now, they have given many the
OL,17,Fchance to get closer to the Titanic
OL,18,Fthan ever before.
